00:15:47,070 --> 00:15:49,250
头更大  够他好好吃一顿了
and an even bigger head, so that was quite a meal.

359
00:15:53,370 --> 00:15:55,750
我爸爸曾给我讲过一个故事
My daddy used to tell me a story

360
00:15:55,760 --> 00:15:59,160
