我家周围也没有一只母鸡
And I certainly never saw a hen around my house,

365
00:16:05,890 --> 00:16:07,270
除非你把我妈也算上
unless you count my mother.

366
00:16:10,200 --> 00:16:12,470
-要我插手吗  -但是  说正经的...
- Do you want me to do something? - But, seriously,

367
00:16:12,480 --> 00:16:14,790
-不用  让他说  -我很爱这座城市...
- No. Let him talk. - ...I do love this town...

368
00:16:14,850 --> 00:16:16,770
我不觉得他会引你出场
I don't know if he's ever going to introduce you.

369
00:16:15,780 --> 00:16:19,030
因为它仍有拓荒者的气质
Because it still has that frontier spirit.

370
00:16:17,430 --> 00:16:19,730
他会的  给他点时间
He will. Just give him time.

371
00:16:19,840 --> 00:16:20,810
都一小时了
It's been an hour.

372
00:16:20,820 --> 00:16:22,800
我们十分钟前就该去卡本代尔了
We were supposed to leave for Carbondale ten minutes ago.

373
00:16:22,810 --> 00:16:24,650
我不能打断他  他可是副总统
I can't interrupt him. He's the Vice President.

374
00:16:24,660 --> 00:16:26,520
我们又不是在宾州边境上
We're not on the edge of Penn's Woods.

375
00:16:30,180 --> 00:16:31,640
我们得把流域法案的经济发展
We need economic development flowcharts

376
00:16:31,650 --> 00:16:34,170
流程图送交泰瑞・乌麦克办公室
for the watershed bill sent over to Terry Womack's office.

377
00:16:34,180 --> 00:16:36,150
-打印稿  20份  -我就去办
- Hard copies, 20 of them. - I'll do it right away.

378
00:16:38,010 --> 00:16:39,480
瑞秋怎么样了
How's everything going with Rachel?

379
00:16:39,920 --> 00:16:41,550
心情不怎么好
I think she's a little down in the dumps.

380
00:16:41,680 --> 00:16:42,950
上周她找到份服务员的工作
She got a waitressing job last week,

381
00:16:42,960 --> 00:16:44,180
