they'll withdraw support.

396
00:17:38,880 --> 00:17:40,600
推测得有点道理
Not an unfair speculation.

397
00:17:42,630 --> 00:17:44,600
我知道你为他的竞选付出了很多
Well, I know how hard you've been working on his campaign,

398
00:17:44,610 --> 00:17:46,950
想给你提个醒
so I wanted to give you a heads-up.

399
00:17:48,510 --> 00:17:50,990
如果她扩大调查告诉我一声
Well, let me know if she expands her inquiry.

400
00:17:51,000 --> 00:17:54,320
-扩大到哪  -你认为值得说的
- Into what? - Anything you deem worth telling.

401
00:17:55,010 --> 00:17:56,340
我能先给她点甜头吗
Well, can I throw her a bone?

402
00:17:56,480 --> 00:17:58,950
如果我透点消息给她  她可能更肯说
She might be more talkative if I have information for her.

403
00:17:58,960 --> 00:18:01,590
-什么样的甜头  -法案的计票结果
- What sort of bone? - The vote count for the bill.

404
00:18:01,600 --> 00:18:03,160
计票还没出来
I don't have a vote count yet.

405
00:18:03,500 --> 00:18:05,690
下午会有个初步结果
Should have a preliminary one this afternoon.

406
00:18:05,960 --> 00:18:08,710
-你会告诉我吗  -有确实消息就告诉你
- You'll let me know? - As soon as I have something solid.

407
00:18:08,850 --> 00:18:09,830
还有件事
There's one more thing.

408
00:18:13,120 --> 00:18:14,240
昨天晚上...
About last night...

409
00:18:14,250 --> 00:18:16,440
不用道歉
Oh, no need to apologize.

410
00:18:16,450 --> 00:18:18,460
你肯定有个充足的理由
I'm sure you had a very good reason.

411
00:18:20,500 --> 00:18:21,230
是的
I do.

412
00:18:23,350 --> 00:18:24,690
我觉得我们不应该继续了
I think we should end it.

413
00:18:26,470 --> 00:18:29,720
不是公事方面  另一方面
Not professionally, the other thing.

414
00:18:38,760 --> 00:18:39,780
为什么是现在
Why now?

415
00:18:39,870 --> 00:18:41,930
我们的工作关系很好
We have a really good working relationship.

416
00:18:42,460 --> 00:18:44,190
我不想搞得过于复杂
I don't wanna overcomplicate that.

417
00:18:45,350 --> 00:18:46,300
可以
All right.

418
00:18:48,330 --> 00:18:50,520
-你没有意见  -完全没有
- You're okay with it? - Completely.

419
00:18:50,560 --> 00:18:51,600
结束了
It's over.

420
00:18:53,850 --> 00:18:56,270
我们之间的合作不会受到影响
And it won't change things in terms of our arrangement?

421
00:18:56,280 --> 00:19:00,320
当然  我不会为一个成熟的决定而惩罚人
Oh, please. I don't punish people for making adult decisions.

422
00:19:03,570 --> 00:19:04,850
谢谢你  弗兰西斯
Thank you, Francis.

423
00:19:13,770 --> 00:19:16,790
她于我微若尘埃
She was never more than a faint blip on my radar.

424
00:19:17,370 --> 00:19:19,150
我们互相利用
We've served each other's purpose.

425
00:19:19,480 --> 00:19:20,840
她想做个成年人
If she wants to be an adult,

426
00:19:21,340 --> 00:19:24,820
就让她看看离巢之后她能飞多远
let her see how she can fly once she leaves the nest.

427
00:19:37,600 --> 00:19:39,670
-克莱尔  -凯瑟琳
- Claire. - Catherine.

428
00:19:42,200 --> 00:19:43,750
谢谢给我时间
Thank you for fitting me in.

429
00:19:43,760 --> 00:19:46,670
对你和弗兰克我总是有空的
Oh, I can always find time for you and Frank.

430
00:19:49,760 --> 00:19:52,200
我来是因为净水计划
Well, the reason I'm here is the C.W.I. has

431
00:19:52,210 --> 00:19:55,170
有一大批滤水器卡在了南苏丹
a large shipment of water filters stuck in South Sudan,

432
00:19:55,180 --> 00:19:58,120
过去四个月一直放在仓库里
and they've been in storage for the past four months,

433
00:19:58,130 --> 00:19:59,900
就放在那儿  苏丹政府...
just sitting there, and the Sudanese government...

434
00:19:59,910 --> 00:20:01,380
不肯让海关放这批货
Won't release the shipments through customs.

435
00:20:01,390 --> 00:20:03,520
我的助理向我汇报了最新进展
My deputy briefed me on the latest.

436
00:20:03,780 --> 00:20:05,060
好  我知道弗兰西斯
Right. And I know that Francis

437
00:20:05,070 --> 00:20:06,570
不久前也跟你提过
spoke to you about this not too long ago,

438
00:20:06,580 --> 00:20:08,810
但最近国务院没有什么消息
but lately we haven't heard much from the state department,

439
00:20:08,820 --> 00:20:09,820
我就想能不能找你帮忙
so I was wondering if you could help.

440
00:20:09,830 --> 00:20:10,990
我们已经尽力了  克莱尔
We've done our best, Claire.

441
00:20:11,000 --> 00:20:12,480
我调了最有能力的人去处理
I put my top people on this.

442
00:20:12,490 --> 00:20:14,510
苏丹那边就是不给回应
The Sudanese are just not responding.

443
00:20:14,730 --> 00:20:16,750
我们还能做些什么吗
Well, is there anything else we can do?

444
00:20:16,760 --> 00:20:19,540
那可是价值超过二十万的设备
There's over $200,000 worth of equipment.

445
00:20:19,550 --> 00:20:21,700
我也想帮你  我知道这对你有多重要
I wish I could. I know how important this is to you,

446
00:20:21,710 --> 00:20:24,000
但我们即将断绝邦交
but we're about to cut off diplomatic ties.

447
00:20:24,010 --> 00:20:25,570
这是总统直接下达的指令
It's a directive straight from the President.

448
00:20:25,580 --> 00:20:28,530
我们无法继续忽视他们违反人权的行为
We can't ignore their human rights violations anymore.

449
00:20:30,230 --> 00:20:31,660
非正式的途径呢
What about back channels?

450
00:20:31,670 --> 00:20:34,070
一旦断绝邦交  无论正式还是非正式
Well, once we cut ties, I can't contact their government

451
00:20:34,080 --> 00:20:35,780
我都不能联系他们的政府
officially or unofficially.

452
00:20:36,880 --> 00:20:38,820
你能帮我联系上什么人吗
Well, is there someone you could put me in touch with?

453
00:20:38,830 --> 00:20:42,160
抱歉  克莱尔  我无能为力
I'm sorry, Claire. My hands are tied.

454
00:20:42,170 --> 00:20:43,510
我愿意为你和弗兰克上刀山
I would move mountains for you and Frank,

455
00:20:43,520 --> 00:20:45,110
但我已经尽力了
but I've done all I can.

456
00:20:48,050 --> 00:20:48,950
当然
Of course.

457
00:20:50,020 --> 00:20:51,850
-见到你很高兴  -我也是
- Okay. Good to see you. - You too.

458
00:20:53,300 --> 00:20:55,080
议员  这周晚些时候
Congressman, you have a major bill

459
00:20:55,090 --> 00:20:56,540
